-- Honda President Ito Says Electric Vehicle Market Is Developing
-- B y
-- 2010-11-18T05:29:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-18/honda-president-ito-says-electric-vehicle-market-is-developing-video.html
Honda Motor Co. President Takanobu 
Ito talks about the outlook for electric cars.  Honda, the first automaker to sell hybrid cars in the U.S.,
plans to enter the battery-vehicle market with an electric Fit 
subcompact in 2012 after hesitating to join in the competition. 
Ito spoke to reporters at the Los Angeles Auto Show yesterday. 
